Name: Freakshow:Anniversary
About the game: Freakshow came out originally August 2017! This is to celebrate the anniversary of the project! You go visit the local circus and he takes you. What will you discover? Major updates compared to the original (2017): -Achievements -Original soundtrack! -Inventory system -Better voice acting -And more! Come play a few puzzles and enjoy the mini games! Thank you for supporting this game through the development!
